I just upgraded to 5.9.7 - it's awesome.

I really love the inline commenting. Small suggestion though (that would make a big difference): When you mention someone in an inline comment, the e-mail that goes through doesn't show the text you've highlighted to comment on. Although it's great that the page link takes you directly to the comment, it'd be yet another bonus to have the highlighted text excerpted in the e-mail. 

Thanks!

